

Amazon Search Framework Requirements 

Test task ProPartner QA Automation
Technology: NodeJS, Selenium Web driver
Implement automated test scenario using mentioned technology stack that validates search functionality of the Amazon web-store.
1. Open Google Chrome browser
2. Go to https://www.amazon.com
3. Input “laptop” to the search box
4. Run search
5. Filter items by price using quick filter “$500-600”
6. Run search
7. Go to the last page
8. Log to console title and price of the penultimate item
 
Write the code so that it is self-sufficient and can be run on any machine.
Add comments to the code explaining the basic steps and actions.
Instructions for installing and running the test should be included in the comments.
